<abstract><t>This memo provides application-specific requirements for the Path Computation Element communication Protocol (PCEP) for the support of Impairments in Wavelength Switched Optical Networks (WSON). From a path computation perspective, optical impairments are additional constraints on the process of determining an optical light path.</t></abstract>

